text: <@U01S1VB9X9P> I recall there was a discussion on here once about how long it took ppl to be profitable (and even a poll i think?) 1 year is far from unusual, if you were to turn profitable right now, you d probably still be on the faster side. Also, that poll will likely include ppl who started way earlier, at times where being profitable via bot was still easier
